## Other Resources

- Bar Plots
	- **Good for:** displaying multiple categories, particularly when there are sub-categories. 
	- <a href="https://support.office.com/en-gb/article/Present-your-data-in-a-bar-chart-6050133e-398e-451b-9fd9-a881cb03cb89" target=_blank>in Excel</a>  
	-  <a href="https://support.google.com/docs/answer/190723?hl=en" target=_blank>in Google Sheets</a>  
- Mosaic Plots
	- **Good for:** quickly seeing the relationship between two or more variables. NOTE: not native to excel OR google sheets, but there is a plugin and a template below that enable use. 
	- <a href="http://www.clearlyandsimply.com/clearly_and_simply/2014/05/marimekko-charts-in-microsoft-excel.html " target=_blank>in Excel</a>  
	-  <a href="https://code.google.com/p/mosaic-plot-gadget/ " target=_blank>in Google Sheets</a>  
	
